Interface TopN<E>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<E>, Iterable<E>, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ListTopN, TreeTopN

    public interface TopN<E>
extends Collection<E>, Serializable
    A generic collection limited to size N. If more than N elements are added, it will keep the greatest N elements only, discarding the others.
    Author:
    Einar Saukas
